{"tid":2082871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於「街工」話唔參選，絕對值得尊重","createTime":"2020-06-28T11:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:52:19.000Z","uid":81236,"like":103,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b6e3f6a1bbbb9468583a4190d9150f97eae2fd","tid":2082871,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"私怨既比五毛分化完未？<br />\n<br />\n參選又話人唔好出黎獻世，舊個套唔得<br />\n<br />\n而家話唔選就話人覺得無機會所以唔選，應該解散<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先不論佢地有冇機會贏<br />\n<br />\n有幾多個植根香港咁多年既黨派/人物係咁早會行出黎話唔選？<br />\n<br />\n立法會本來就係咩人都參選得，如果再派梁耀忠同民主派協調無話一定一席都冇<br />\n<br />\n佢地個套係現今香港政治已經真係舊<br />\n<br />\n願意接受並作出改善係值得尊重<br />\n<br />\n尊注去地區工作反而啱返佢地政黨取向<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔係一幅坐定粒六既樣去選<br />\n<br />\n如果大家再沉迷係私怨<br />\n<br />\n永遠都辦法達成團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bec194bfc3a92b3f69b648128ee5ae371234ac6","tid":2082871,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fcf97e314ad8d9358b3311649e00279ba2d662","tid":2082871,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:08:50.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd29b94a20d141f21ea75ae449cc7886bde6a6b5","tid":2082871,"uid":227788,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"咁都證明咗佢哋唔係收人錢<br />\n純粹係真正on9"},{"pid":"330dd63cb596d14a74a325f59e098ef362c7980f","tid":2082871,"uid":39092,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bd29b94a20d141f21ea75ae449cc7886bde6a6b5","tid":2082871,"uid":227788,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"咁都證明咗佢哋唔係收人錢<br />\n純粹係真正on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"雖然真係好on9<br />\n不過respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bfd110996e4addeb598ba09079e14f9db00fb4","ti